  "texts": [
    "Their experiments in the Overcooked-AI environment with a human proxy model and real humans found that their method outperformed existing learning-based approaches.",
    "Brawer et al. [9] proposed a preliminary design for a natural language interface for a task assignment system using an LLM, which they plan to evaluate in the Overcooked environment.",
    "Verma et al. [73] investigated using LLMs to serve as effective human proxies by capturing human preferences for collaborating with AI agents.",
    "They explored the ability of LLMs to model mental states and understand human reasoning processes in Overcooked.",
    "Liu et al. [41] proposed a hierarchical language agent for human-AI coordination in Overcooked to provide both strong reasoning abilities and real-time execution."
  ],
